    Class Description
    BotBlockAPI
    Class used to define the auth-tokens used for the different sites.
    BotBlockAPI.Builder
    Builder class to create an instance of BotBlockAPI
    DeprecatedSince
    Annotation used to indicate since when a method or field is deprecated.
    GetAction Deprecated.
    Use GetBotAction for Bot related and GetListAction for List related actions.
    GetBotAction
    Class used to perform GET actions on the /bots/:id endpoint.
    GetListAction
    Class used to perform GET actions on the /lists endpoint.
    GetListAction.ApiField
    Enum containing the different API fields a bot list may have.
    PostAction
    Class to perform post actions with.
    RatelimitedException
    Indicates that the Java-Wrapper (Bot) was rate-limited by BotBlock.org (Received error code 429)
    The returned error message contains the route, Bot ID, IP and delay for when rate limit is removed.
    Site
    Enum class containing all sites currently supported by BotBlock.org.
